based on a Lyapunov-Schmidt reduction strategy applied\nto a momentum space formulation. The PN barrier bounds require appropriate\nuniform decay estimates for the discrete Fourier transform of DNLS discrete\nsolitary waves. A key role is also played by non-degeneracy of the ground state\nof FNLS, recently proved by Frank, Lenzmann \\& Silvestre.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 16:46:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 22:29:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
