trics (F-measure and G-mean), only the three\nsampling techniques are considered as good performing (i.e., LRO, SMOTE, and\nSMOTERandRep).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 23:31:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
