s take the values $\\Delta^{p,p'}_{r,s-\\frac12}$ where\n$\\Delta^{p,p'}_{r,s}$ is given by the usual Kac formula. The $(r,s)$ Robin\nboundary conditions are thus conjugate to scaling operators with half-integer\nvalues for the Kac label $s-\\mbox{$\\textstyle \\frac{1}{2}$}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 23:59:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Apr 2017 12:10:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-04"}
